of Contents</button></div></div><div class="px-2"><div class="overflow-auto md:h-[calc(100vh-8.5rem)] h-[calc(100vh-4rem)] rounded bg-surface"><div class="rounded px-2 pb-8 max-w-readable mx-auto"><div data-state="active" data-orientation="horizontal" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="radix-_R_2npfqt6btb_-trigger-toc" id="radix-_R_2npfqt6btb_-content-toc" tabindex="0" data-slot="tabs-content" class="ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 px-2 mt-1.5" style="animation-duration:0s"><div><div class="w-full py-2 text-sm font-light text-foreground flex gap-2 mt-6"><div class="size-5 text-primary-200 [&amp;_svg]:stroke-1 [&amp;_svg]:size-5 my-auto"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-library-big"><rect width="8" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="1"></rect><path d="M7 3v18"></path><path d="M20.4 18.9c.2.5-.1 1.1-.6 1.3l-1.9.7c-.5.2-1.1-.1-1.3-.6L11.1 5.1c-.2-.5.1-1.1.6-1.3l1.9-.7c.5-.2 1.1.1 1.3.6Z"></path></svg></div><span class="my-auto font-light">General Sūtra Section</span></div><div class="w-full py-2 text-sm font-light text-foreground flex gap-2"><div class="size-5 text-primary-200 [&amp;_svg]:stroke-1 [&amp;_svg]:size-5 my-auto"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-book-open"><path d="M12 7v14"></path><path d="M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"></path></svg></div><span class="my-auto font-semibold">Unraveling the Intent</span></div><div class="flex gap-2"><div class="size-5 text-primary-200 [&amp;_svg]:stroke-1 [&amp;_svg]:size-5 my-auto"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2