\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"characterized as, characterized by, consisting in, constituted\",\"tibetan\":\"རབ་ཏུ་ཕྱེ་བ།, རབ་ཏུ་ཕྱེ་བ།, རབ་ཏུ་ཕྱེ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"prabhāvita, prabhāvita, prabhāvita\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"rab tu phye ba, rab tu phye ba, rab tu phye ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"afc53781-0387-4f04-916f-8cd48b06c476\",\"authority\":\"3608013f-f69c-43b7-a317-dcd0f8128401\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eAlso translated here as “\u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-049-001-1348\\\"\u003echaracterized by\u003c/span\u003e” and “\u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-049-001-1380\\\"\u003econstituted\u003c/span\u003e.” See Schmithausen 2014, p. 557, §512.1. \u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"characterized as, characterized by, consisting in, constituted\",\"tibetan\":\"རབ་ཏུ་ཕྱེ་བ།, རབ་ཏུ་ཕྱེ་བ།, རབ་ཏུ་ཕྱེ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"prabhāvita, prabhāvita, prabhāvita\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"rab tu phye ba, rab tu phye ba, rab tu phye ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"fa830996-9c11-4cc4-9e78-6790a6dbb583\",\"authority\":\"3608013f-f69c-43b7-a317-dcd0f8128401\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eSee Schmithausen 2014, p. 557, §512.1. Also translated here as “\u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-049-001-1348\\\"\u003echaracterized by\u003c/span\u003e” and “\u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-049-001-1376\\\"\u003econsisting in\u003c/span\u003e.”\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"characterized as, characterized by, consisting in, constituted\",\"tibetan\":\"རབ་ཏུ་ཕྱེ་བ།, རབ་ཏུ་ཕྱེ་བ།, རབ་ཏུ་ཕྱེ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"prabhāvita, prabhāvita, prabhāvita\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"rab tu phye ba, rab tu phye ba, rab tu phye ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"b667709c-9e2a-4877-96d5-8b056867ac96\",\"authority\":\"5edda6f4-289b-47d4-80e8-932287e9ad32\",\"definition\":\"\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"citta, mind\",\"tibetan\":\"སེམས།\",\"sanskrit\":\"citta\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chi