trs\":{\"start\":186,\"end\":200},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"53a21c77-8b16-459a-b409-c3086bb96cbd\",\"uuid\":\"bf02bfb1-cce8-4f03-b98c-31f424a410d4\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" through the three aspects of basis, path, and result in order to solve seeming contradictions and quandaries in doctrines that were of primary importance for followers of the Great Vehicle (e.g., the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":200,\"end\":401}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"two truths\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":401,\"end\":411},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"a0dea610-3170-45d1-8066-2121a1ad810f\",\"uuid\":\"c6250705-d77e-46f7-83f1-d70212c13c11\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" in chapter 3 and meditative practice in chapter 8). Now, if we read the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":411,\"end\":484}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Saṃdhi­nirmocana\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":484,\"end\":500},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"672aa951-866a-4521-a6da-6d5ebcc97b63\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"type\":\"inlineTitle\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" as a single text, we have to confront the web of meaning found in this text in its entirety with the web of meaning of the target culture in order to avoid potential misunderstandings.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":500,\"end\":685}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"fb0e23b8-0657-45bd-86d1-9b8b45a2d814\",\"sort\":2159,\"type\":\"introduction\",\"label\":\"i.58\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":1071,\"uuid\":\"fb0e23b8-0657-45bd-86d1-9b8b45a2d814\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"This operation has a major impact on the translation of some key terms, such as \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":80}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"vijñaptimātra\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":80,\"end\":93},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"8fe6483c-7a2f-4114-886e-1185bf09c76d\",\"uuid\":\"d0ff6486-1227-4e1a-a303-48f0f7c5185d\",\"toh\":null,\"start\":80,\"end\":0}},{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":80,\"end\":93,\"uuid\":\"fed5fdf8-44cc-4862-82e9-10f5da295a4f\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Since idealism (in the sense that \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":93,\"end\":129}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"mind\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":129,\"end\":133},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b667709c-9e2a-4877-96d5-8b056867ac96\",\"uuid\":\"7e43d5b0-e1b6-4614-916f-36507490d5e6\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is an unchanging \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":133,\"end\":151}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"essence\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":151,\"end\":158},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"47c8923c-56be-43d8-b398-ff4290cece41\",\"uuid\":\"8ac122b0-1a2c-4963-9f17-91256fe5d648\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\") is not an option given the teaching imparted in this sūtra, I tried to avoid any potential \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":158,\"end\":251}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"confusion\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":251,\"end\":260},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"6cd964f3-8507-4616-b59f-03c70b37f614\",\"uuid\":\"591f9bdd-f63d-4214-b7dd-ccc48ef5e7a4\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" resulting from an unfortunate choice of terminology. In a word, I would rather stay on the safe side than insert in my translation a potentially misleading term. As a consequence, I decided to translate \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":260,\"end\":464}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"vijñaptimātra\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":464,\"end\":477},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"8fe6483c-7a2f-4114-886e-1185bf09c76d\",\"uuid\":\"3e235070-cd6d-4248-80fb-3a57740469b9\",\"toh\":null,\"start\":464,\"end\":0}},{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":464,\"end\":477,\"uuid\":\"673fee4a-854a-423a-97d9-083bc18e24bb\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" as “a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":477,\"end\":484}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"mere representation\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":484,\"end\":503},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"8fe6483c-7a2f-4114-886e-1185bf09c76d\",\"uuid\":\"7ddaf856-44ef-40a6-970c-9886bb709b32\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"” instead of using nominalizations such as “\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":503,\"end\":547}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"cognition\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":547,\"end\":556},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"2f9b275a-4384-48e1-82d5-36ad42fe9878\",\"uuid\":\"fbcc78a8-5a22-4ca0-9f9a-2e5af50e4e21\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"-only.” The first expression is relatively unambiguous in the target culture as it minimizes the risk of misunderstanding the message of the text. Another option would be “just a representation.” These formulations mitigate the risk of superimposing an \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":556,\"end\":809}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"essence\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":809,\"end\":816},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"47c8923c-56be-43d8-b398-ff4290cece41\",\"uuid\":\"7481dec1-d52d-49d1-9ebf-fc2f842a8d94\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" on what is meant by \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":816,\"end\":837}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"vijñapti\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":837,\"end\":845},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":837,\"end\":845,\"uuid\":\"522ab3f3-2acf-4dae-903e-d3b2a2931c5f\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":845,\"end\":846},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"6c215b77-5bbe-402b-bab8-8bc482239db8\",\"label\":\"33\",\"uuid\":\"65a02776-7ac3-4cbd-800c-dcd15afc67b4\",\"start\":846,\"end\":846,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" The formulation “\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":846,\"end\":864}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"cognition\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":864,\"end\":873},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"2f9b275a-4384-48e1-82d5-36ad42fe9878\",\"uuid\":\"83342102-a913-4d46-9053-14b5569883f5\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"-only” in the sense of “pure \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":873,\"end\":902}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"cognition\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":902,\"end\":911},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"2f9b275a-4384-48e1-82d5-36ad42fe9878\",\"uuid\":\"12a44d3b-af81-4b92-9217-a77a70d51fa4\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"” is in contrast ambivalent. It could also (but not necessarily) signify that only \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":911,\"end\":994}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"cognition\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":994,\"end\":1003},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"2f9b275a-4384-48e1-82d5-36ad42fe9878\",\"uuid\":\"349ee988-5a92-4013-89f8-d01f4e03635c\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" truly exists and by extension, that only \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1003,\"end\":1045}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"mind\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1045,\"end\":1049},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b667709c-9e2a-4877-96d5-8b056867ac96\",\"uuid\":\"96873f17-4527-45c7-b6ba-2a90ebb53e1f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" exists as an \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1049,\"end\":1063}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"essence\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1063,\"end\":1070},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"47c8923c-56be-43d8-b398-ff4290cece41\",\"uuid\":\"0f5297c2-1753-43bc-bd63-1e1f162e2c1a\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1070,\"end\":1071}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"e411b741-2629-4f8a-a39e-726b8b1c1772\",\"sort\":2191,\"type\":\"introduction\",\"label\":\"i.59\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":1633,\"uuid\":\"e411b741-2629-4f8a-a39e-726b8b1c1772\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"In the last step of the translation process, Billeter recommends that translators perform various operations aiming at polishing the translation, such as replicating the possible effects of semantic resonance throughout the text, improving the connection between sentences and paragraphs, modifying the order of clauses, solving problems of euphony, or editing the translation to make it clearer and simpler by chunking long sentences or eliminating repetitions. To illustrate one of these various tasks in the context of the present project, I decided to review all the terminology pertaining to the semantic field of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":619}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"insight\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":619,\"end\":626},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b8a50087-18c2-468e-a3a0-0e23baf58acd\",\"uuid\":\"bdc31f10-a91d-490e-a871-04798dbbe7e9\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" (\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":626,\"end\":628}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"vipaśyanā\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":628,\"end\":637},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":628,\"end\":637,\"uuid\":\"50921bd9-ff27-4b86-814f-0a311edb884f\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\") after I had finished translating the entire text. I took as a starting point \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":637,\"end\":716}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"8.4\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":716,\"end\":719},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"internalLink\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"d6c2f6b9-b334-4568-a978-54f29cf9e019\",\"href\":\"/entity/passage/592ea05c-485b-42aa-bff3-17af26bdb2c2\",\"entity\":\"592ea05c-485b-42aa-bff3-17af26bdb2c2\",\"type\":\"passage\",\"toh\":null,\"isSameWork\":true,\"subtype\":\"translation\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", in which \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":719,\"end\":730}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"vipaśyanā\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":730,\"end\":739},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":730,\"end\":739,\"uuid\":\"d7063912-87d1-4374-919d-77525ed14d37\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is defined by means of a series of technical terms, such as \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":739,\"end\":800}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"pratyavekṣaṇa\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":800,\"end\":813},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"a0849c8e-a301-4513-9fb5-6d97229d1a4c\",\"uuid\":\"aa4e4f39-1c3f-4af1-88db-862d53c087bf\",\"toh\":null,\"start\":800,\"end\":0}},{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":800,\"end\":813,\"uuid\":\"8605b7e2-848d-413c-b62b-f3eb63b63c8e\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":813,\"end\":815}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"vibhājanā\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":815,\"end\":824},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"a2901304-6ccb-4623-ac9f-79c0293e44a3\",\"uuid\":\"3c8d393c-a789-4e5e-a5cf-c1ce98efd4a9\",\"toh\":null,\"start\":815,\"end\":0}},{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":815,\"end\":824,\"uuid\":\"fe73e937-5dd9-43fa-820a-828c8d995c39\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":824,\"end\":826}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"pravicaya\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":826,\"end\":835},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":826,\"end\":835,\"uuid\":\"52a15e62-6a35-4dd5-bc56-ac8a9d56d927\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}},{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"8fb62f7f-1ea7-435e-b5ca-f36314dea7e9\",\"uuid\":\"65d68e18-6952-472b-baf3-5d22cd9cdf23\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":835,\"end\":837}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"paritarka\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":837,\"end\":846},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ef971d85-9939-43c2-b733-f361b9528c88\",\"uuid\":\"f0d1bbbc-e442-4870-aa57-71daf16adceb\",\"toh\":null,\"start\":837,\"end\":0}},{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":837,\"end\":846,\"uuid\":\"0072aca1-e5bd-4c88-8e09-d66d24a8217c\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":846,\"end\":848}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"parimīmāṃsā\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":848,\"end\":859},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"c15924e0-c0e9-4625-b1e3-37c2789f9775\",\"uuid\":\"48971318-46f6-448e-8ec3-2b4aeb81ec6c\",\"toh\":null,\"start\":848,\"end\":0}},{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":848,\"end\":859,\"uuid\":\"a08a7eb4-dcb8-4c7c-9733-987d4785a811\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":859,\"end\":861}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"nitīraṇa\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":861,\"end\":869},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bddb0c1a-c339-4394-8d79-bb80288cd87e\",\"uuid\":\"af7ea32c-76f3-4085-96ac-e4323d0b0911\",\"toh\":null,\"start\":861,\"end\":0}},{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":861,\"end\":869,\"uuid\":\"9ab1dcf6-9e1e-4f18-b3d0-b333e9106046\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":869,\"end\":875}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"vitarka\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":875,\"end\":882},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":875,\"end\":882,\"uuid\":\"1bd62a6f-6008-447a-8518-5c1c7f4a4d26\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}},{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b260d4ed-1d68-4114-a625-827ee94e4053\",\"uuid\":\"93e7b5b2-1792-489e-b961-42a15bbc4e95\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". I first tried to find the best translation for each term in the context of this chapter. Next, I checked the usage of all these terms and other related concepts (e.g., \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":882,\"end\":1052}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"pratisaṃkhyā\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1052,\"end\":1064},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1052,\"end\":1064,\"uuid\":\"bca8549f-8bf1-45b5-8337-28a135c40337\",\"type\":\"span\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"textStyle\":\"foreign\"}},{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"60bbf8d8-91e4-4413-8a02-edbdb0ad89b0\",\"uuid\":\"23934ad2-c51e-4fd0-9fd7-95246801fa79\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\") throughout the text to standardize the corresponding English terminology. I also tried to minimize the use of square brackets indicating additions to the text when these additions were logically implied by the source text. A typology of such situations would include various operations, such as breaking down a compound, clarifying an abbreviated form corresponding to a well-attested collocation, stating a logical subject, object, or verb that is elided in the source text, mentioning the number of a technical term that usually comes as a list of individual items.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1064,\"end\":1633}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"5c4c8ecd-2d41-4412-8f8b-dc5f24a544a7\",\"sort\":2219,\"type\":\"introduction\",\"label\":\"i.60\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":481,\"uuid\":\"5c4c8ecd-2d41-4412-8f8b-dc5f24a544a7\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Through all these operations, my aim has been to maximize both accuracy and readability while maintaining the consistency of the very systematic presentation of the Great Vehicle developed in the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":196}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Saṃdhi­nirmocana­sūtra\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":196,\"end\":218},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"fb92777c-5392-419f-98cb-d2d0e008f95e\",\"lang\":\"Sa-Ltn\",\"type\":\"inlineTitle\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". This text is important in this spiritual tradition since it condenses all aspects of Mahāyāna. I hope that this translation will contribute to improve our understanding of the interplay between \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":218,\"end\":414}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"liberation\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":414,\"end\":424},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"329707c5-9855-4bfd-8094-023a57e9c0cc\",\"uuid\":\"237c0738-24d5-4a47-9830-20c74f27ab99\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" as a path and primordial freedom as the ground of being.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":424,\"end\":481}}]}]}],\"body\":[{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"c9b19f93-a6e1-47d8-9d0b-15f729cd3d9f\",\"sort\":2220,\"type\":\"translationHeader\",\"label\":null,\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"start\":0,\"end\":15,\"uuid\":\"7892cbbc-5b48-48a8-bd72-ad2182c71bb0\",\"class\":\"section-title\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Translation\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":15}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"e776c6fb-acb3-49e4-b98f-f80a7a0b00a3\",\"sort\":2221,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"\",\"alignments\":{\"toh106\":{\"folioUuid\":\"89fc8369-baea-49bc-95cc-da30e939e887\",\"toh\":\"toh106\",\"tibetan\":\"༄༅༅། །རྒྱ་གར་སྐད་དུ། ཨཱརྱ་སན་དྷི་ནིར་མོ་ཙ་ན་ནཱ་མ་མ་ཧཱ་ཡཱ་ན་སཱུ་ཏྲ། བོད་སྐད་དུ། འཕགས་པ་དགོངས་པ་ངེས་པར་འགྲེལ་པ་ཞེས་བྱ་བ་ཐེག་པ་ཆེན་པོའི་\\nམདོ། \",\"folioNumber\":1,\"volumeNumber\":49}}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":30,\"uuid\":\"6aa526e4-d687-481b-a213-05f0614b30d4\",\"level\":2,\"class\":\"body-title-honorific\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"64fc9e8f-674f-4190-88ec-7092aac74de3\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The Noble Great Vehicle Sūtra \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":30}}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":30,\"end\":51,\"uuid\":\"8aef6242-98dc-473d-ace1-ae9815a3b0e4\",\"level\":2,\"class\":\"body-title-main\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Unraveling the Intent\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":30,\"end\":51}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"e306857d-5244-4100-ac6b-23e6c65cb43b\",\"sort\":2229,\"type\":\"prologueHeader\",\"label\":\"p.\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":3,\"start\":0,\"end\":8,\"uuid\":\"aa213b01-5a28-497d-9850-e83a7d4ff49a\",\"class\":\"section-title\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Prologue\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":8}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"fba6f058-6392-4540-bb34-ce6f6077481b\",\"sort\":2232,\"type\":\"prologue\",\"label\":\"p.1\",\"alignments\":{\"toh106\":{\"folioUuid\":\"89fc8369-baea-49bc-95cc-da30e939e887\",\"toh\":\"toh106\",\"tibetan\":\"$7c\",\"folioNumber\":1,\"volumeNumber\":49}},\"invalid\":true},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":40,\"uuid\":\"547f1b96-500c-45ae-a03d-364c67ae327f\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"894da4e4-2bfa-4dc8-b2d1-b7e06861f8ed\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Homage to all buddhas and bodhisattvas! \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":40}}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":40,\"end\":1429},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Thus did I hear at one time. The \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":40,\"end\":73}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Blessed One\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":73,\"end\":84},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"1b51c11a-be57-45e7-82eb-2691bb785c0d\",\"uuid\":\"759c4f42-d187-4f84-bcf7-58e3fbe92b9b\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" was dwelling in an unfathomable palace, built with the blazing \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":84,\"end\":148}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"seven precious substances\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":148,\"end\":173},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"c2db67b6-42db-4c9c-afbc-ad237b9e450d\",\"uuid\":\"98246d04-de63-426a-a2f1-bac647b4f6e1\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\",\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":173,\"end\":174},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"0e767ac6-fc81-44ef-b8b7-03fee591e802\",\"label\":\"34\",\"uuid\":\"66c1db2d-6c4e-45d9-ab14-039c45efdf9b\",\"start\":174,\"end\":174,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" that emitted\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":174,\"end\":187},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"8719cfbd-072b-4d01-85c7-bdfd043a6db2\",\"label\":\"35\",\"uuid\":\"dc89b4ff-557e-4ecf-8077-42da5f6ecd15\",\"start\":187,\"end\":187,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" great light rays suffusing countless universes.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":187,\"end\":235},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"5cf70914-20a3-4e87-ab4a-a70c29fe4720\",\"label\":\"36\",\"uuid\":\"0d797230-9bc6-4a22-bc47-afd5f2dbfa2c\",\"start\":235,\"end\":235,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Each of its \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":235,\"end\":248}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"rooms\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":248,\"end\":253},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"160c3de6-a6b2-44c9-befb-bbe0753c4b47\",\"uuid\":\"20fd48ae-4bcd-4716-8685-7d043c7536bb\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" was well arranged and its design was infinite. It was the undivided maṇḍala, the domain transcending the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":253,\"end\":359}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"three worlds\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":359,\"end\":371},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"a7fa4f