ss gods, \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":572,\"end\":665}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"nāgas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":665,\"end\":670},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"2468b23c-6789-4da5-aa73-40a87a8fdf00\",\"uuid\":\"e9d6de06-f91c-443b-be48-21ba3df094ef\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":670,\"end\":672}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"yakṣas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":672,\"end\":678},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"c111f176-89d6-4bfc-9b2a-9b3756cabef1\",\"uuid\":\"d65a912b-d902-40bd-8f61-a21882ebf338\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":678,\"end\":680}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"gandharvas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":680,\"end\":690},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"2432c308-6920-44c5-ad61-a308599ff0bb\",\"uuid\":\"e1c3f642-25e7-4470-96b2-dc173de07dab\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", demigods, \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":690,\"end\":702}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"garuḍas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":702,\"end\":709},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e4eb082c-79ea-4002-bdb4-3b4549a31c73\",\"uuid\":\"fae79370-057c-470a-905b-fdbbd26554ad\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":709,\"end\":711}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"kinnaras\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":711,\"end\":719},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b63e4eab-dd3f-456e-9620-cc0bdf87a46b\",\"uuid\":\"56c6faa0-084d-4d22-b866-bd3fc9638feb\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":719,\"end\":721}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"mahoragas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":721,\"end\":730},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"c54a5e3f-48fb-4f8b-962d-7af79365eda5\",\"uuid\":\"b778a416-29f6-4639-abfa-19163976ab86\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", humans, and nonhumans. Supported by the great \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":730,\"end\":778}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"joy\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":778,\"end\":781},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"3594f47d-ff91-4b21-bd7c-82d556493a8b\",\"uuid\":\"cbc27036-3607-4ec1-88ed-dc8c682f3438\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and bliss of savoring the Dharma and designed to accomplish the complete welfare of all \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":781,\"end\":870}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"beings\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":870,\"end\":876},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ad3097fe-b272-4d95-8811-3cbb3824ee9e\",\"uuid\":\"ff0e0558-ed42-4601-8fc4-d8138874a927\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", it was free of any harm caused by the stains of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":876,\"end\":926}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"afflictions\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":926,\"end\":937},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"096578ea-4bc4-49a3-b39c-bb89d277b3ef\",\"uuid\":\"6fa5b68c-308a-4c48-b855-4f2daaf0cc5d\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and clear of any demon. Surpassing all manifestations, this unfathomable palace was displayed by the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":937,\"end\":1039}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sovereign power\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1039,\"end\":1054},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"d8dc547d-0e98-408b-bd49-c404b9e0782b\",\"uuid\":\"b99112ef-54e0-4845-8947-14d46ef56113\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" of the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1054,\"end\":1062}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Tathāgata\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1062,\"end\":1071},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"8bf0a239-7fda-4995-8cc7-36b960a1507a\",\"uuid\":\"22ce5743-5b76-4380-b08a-d471b5de6a33\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1071,\"end\":1073}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Mindfulness\",\